CommentBody:
In today's meeting, we talked about the upgrade.
We make a copy of the job folder and the web config file
We took some screenshots of the current settings.
The customer could not download the software under My-Products; there was no product to download.
I provide a direct link to download the application
In the next meeting, we will uninstall the StealthAUDIT 11.0 version and install the 11.6 version.
We will also update AIC and Activity Monitor to the latest version.

In today's meeting, we resolved the issue with the Published Report by adding the customer's account as an administrator to the Access.
We discovered that the FS_BrokenInheritance job has not been run since the last meeting. It is scheduled to run on the 24th of this month.

I upgraded the customer from the StealthAUDIT 11.0 version to the 11.6 version.
I also upgraded the AIC and the Activity Monitor to the latest version.
